.. NEURON documentation master file

The NEURON Simulator
====================

**NEURON** is the world's most widely used simulator for biophysically detailed models of
neurons and networks. It runs efficiently on your laptop, in the cloud, or on HPC clusters
with GPU acceleration. Build and simulate models using **Python**, **HOC**, or NEURON's
graphical interface.

